docs {
  # Create Project
  
  **Description:**
  Creates a new project entry. Requires authentication.
  
  ---
  
  ### Request
  
  **Method:** `POST`
  **URL:** `{{base_url}}{{endPointApi}}/projects/`
  
  **Authentication:**
  - Required: bearer token
  
  **Body Parameters:**
  | Param | Type | Required | Description |
  | :--- | :--- | :---: | :--- |
  | `title` | String | Yes | Project title |
  | `tabName` | String | Yes | Tab/group name |
  | `description` | String | Yes | Short description |
  | `content` | String | Yes | Full content |
  | `stack` | Array/String | Yes | Stack list |
  | `UrlGithub` | String | Yes | GitHub URL |
  | `UrlProject` | String | No | Live project URL |
  | `published` | Number | No | 0 or 1 |
  | `gallery` | Array | No | Asset IDs |
  
  ---
  
  ### Response (201)
  
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Project created successfully",
    "data": {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "New Project",
      "tabName": "portfolio",
      "description": "Short project description",
      "content": "Longer project content",
      "stack": ["Node.js", "TypeScript"],
      "UrlGithub": "https://github.com/example/repo",
      "UrlProject": "https://example.com",
      "published": 0,
      "gallery": ["asset-id-1", "asset-id-2"]
    },
    "timestamp": "2026-01-19T18:39:21.316Z"
  }
  ```
